node.title: Appeal for sightings of missing 10yo Dunedin girl, 'significant concerns' for her welfare
node.description: She went missing from a south Dunedin property on Wednesday.
node.content: ["There are \"significant concerns\" for the welfare of a 10-year-old girl who's been reported missing and authorities are appealing for any sightings of her.\n", "Harlow was reported missing from a property in south Dunedin on Wednesday. She was last seen at about 5pm and was wearing a pink and white 'Champion' branded hoodie and peach and white coloured tie-dye shorts.", "She's described as caucasian, of thin build, with medium-length blonde hair, police said in a statement on Thursday morning.", "There were \"significant concerns\" for her wellbeing and anyone with information on her whereabouts is urged to call 111 immediately, quoting file number 220105/2971."]
